# Monsters/Codex/ — home for the Codex queries/UI-facing collection code, which
# folds into the Monsters assembly (no asmdef of its own). Tracked-but-empty: git
# cannot track an empty directory, and without this file a fresh clone would orphan
# Codex.meta (Unity deletes the meta → dirty working tree + GUID churn). Code lands
# with Epic 2 (CodexService etc.).
